1
00:00:08,148 --> 00:00:09,268
What are you doing?

2
00:01:04,507 --> 00:01:05,467
You punk!

3
00:01:16,747 --> 00:01:17,708
It's fine.

4
00:01:18,267 --> 00:01:19,228
I'm right here.

5
00:01:25,747 --> 00:01:26,588
It's fine.

6
00:01:46,688 --> 00:01:49,888
=The Glory Fades=

7
00:01:49,888 --> 00:01:52,672
=Episode 23=
(Entanglement)

8
00:01:58,547 --> 00:01:59,107
Hello.

9
00:01:59,547 --> 00:02:00,668
Mr. He,

10
00:02:00,827 --> 00:02:01,987
hello there.

11
00:02:02,187 --> 00:02:03,028
Who are you?

12
00:02:03,428 --> 00:02:04,467
First,

13
00:02:04,467 --> 00:02:06,508
congratulations
on your recent promotion.

14
00:02:07,467 --> 00:02:09,508
But that promotion

15
00:02:09,668 --> 00:02:12,508
came at the cost of your son's life.

16
00:02:12,747 --> 00:02:14,428
Wasn't that too high a price?

17
00:02:14,548 --> 00:02:15,268
Who are you?

18
00:02:15,268 --> 00:02:16,388
What do you want?

19
00:02:16,388 --> 00:02:17,548
Tell me, or I'm hanging up.

20
00:02:17,787 --> 00:02:18,787
Mr. He,

21
00:02:19,308 --> 00:02:21,148
don't be so quick to hang up.

22
00:02:21,467 --> 00:02:23,347
Don't repay kindness with hostility.

23
00:02:23,627 --> 00:02:25,507
I sent to you

24
00:02:25,667 --> 00:02:27,868
that clear screenshot

25
00:02:28,032 --> 00:02:29,747
from Cong's accident scene.

26
00:02:33,067 --> 00:02:34,467
There's no need

27
00:02:34,627 --> 00:02:36,388
to be so cryptic with me.

28
00:02:36,588 --> 00:02:37,947
It's all in the past.

29
00:02:38,187 --> 00:02:39,548
I'm not seeking revenge.

30
00:02:41,227 --> 00:02:42,148
Is that so?

31
00:02:42,268 --> 00:02:44,704
On the day of the Beauty Contest,

32
00:02:44,704 --> 00:02:46,667
why did you rush over
to Deep In The Bustle

33
00:02:46,667 --> 00:02:48,828
because of a mysterious call?

34
00:02:49,187 --> 00:02:50,708
You even splurged to

35
00:02:50,828 --> 00:02:52,907
buy drinks for An Ruoxi's

36
00:02:53,148 --> 00:02:54,148
little sister

37
00:02:54,268 --> 00:02:55,787
and interrogate Qin Wei

38
00:02:55,787 --> 00:02:57,108
using Nie Feng's name.

39
00:02:57,388 --> 00:02:58,667
That call was from you?

40
00:02:59,388 --> 00:03:00,187
Who else?

41
00:03:01,347 --> 00:03:02,187
Not many people

42
00:03:02,187 --> 00:03:04,227
in this world know about

43
00:03:04,227 --> 00:03:05,868
the relationship between Su Yunian

44
00:03:05,868 --> 00:03:06,868
and An Ruoxi.

45
00:03:07,467 --> 00:03:08,388
Lucky for me,

46
00:03:08,708 --> 00:03:09,627
I know.

47
00:03:10,467 --> 00:03:11,828
And even luckier,

48
00:03:12,388 --> 00:03:14,108
now so do you.

49
00:03:17,627 --> 00:03:18,988
I went that day

50
00:03:19,428 --> 00:03:20,627
just out of curiosity.

51
00:03:21,148 --> 00:03:23,067
Their relationship
has nothing to do with me.

52
00:03:23,627 --> 00:03:25,588
My son is already dead.

53
00:03:26,667 --> 00:03:27,467
Stop

54
00:03:28,067 --> 00:03:29,787
wasting your effort here.

55
00:03:29,828 --> 00:03:31,467
I think you want to,

56
00:03:31,467 --> 00:03:33,067
but you don't dare.

57
00:03:33,187 --> 00:03:34,588
Because you know

58
00:03:34,880 --> 00:03:38,388
who the three brothers
behind Deep In The Bustle are.

59
00:03:38,588 --> 00:03:40,907
You know how you crawled your way up

60
00:03:40,907 --> 00:03:42,227
step by step.

61
00:03:42,428 --> 00:03:43,627
That's why you don't dare.

62
00:03:43,787 --> 00:03:45,408
You're terrified of losing

63
00:03:45,408 --> 00:03:47,467
everything you have now.

64
00:03:47,667 --> 00:03:48,868
Am I right,

65
00:03:49,347 --> 00:03:50,347
Mayor He?

66
00:03:51,588 --> 00:03:52,747
Who are you, really?

67
00:03:53,148 --> 00:03:54,227
Me?

68
00:03:56,428 --> 00:04:01,067
I'm the leader among the three brothers

69
00:04:01,747 --> 00:04:03,907
at Deep In The Bustle.

70
00:04:07,627 --> 00:04:08,388
Are you saying

71
00:04:08,988 --> 00:04:10,067
you're Nie Feng?

72
00:04:25,867 --> 00:04:26,828
Well.

73
00:04:27,347 --> 00:04:28,427
A nice place.

74
00:04:28,588 --> 00:04:29,467
Quite down-to-earth.

75
00:04:30,148 --> 00:04:31,388
What else, Madam?

76
00:04:31,748 --> 00:04:32,987
We need to eat too, you know.

77
00:04:36,667 --> 00:04:37,227
What?

78
00:04:37,907 --> 00:04:39,028
Did I get the title wrong?

79
00:04:39,588 --> 00:04:41,148
Is there a problem with that?

80
00:04:41,427 --> 00:04:43,028
I can't call her Mrs. Tu.

81
00:04:43,667 --> 00:04:44,828
This is just...

82
00:04:45,307 --> 00:04:45,987
A bit...

83
00:04:47,547 --> 00:04:48,347
But you're right.

84
00:04:48,787 --> 00:04:49,427
No problem.

85
00:04:49,427 --> 00:04:50,068
Fits perfectly.

86
00:04:50,467 --> 00:04:51,188
Not wrong.

87
00:04:59,227 --> 00:04:59,787
Mr. Tu,

88
00:05:02,748 --> 00:05:05,227
this whole mess is entirely my fault.

89
00:05:06,028 --> 00:05:07,347
I almost made

90
00:05:07,708 --> 00:05:08,467
you two

91
00:05:08,748 --> 00:05:09,467
come to blows.

92
00:05:11,188 --> 00:05:11,987
My fault.

93
00:05:15,360 --> 00:05:16,388
Look at him.

94
00:05:17,188 --> 00:05:18,547
The one hitting has a stern face.

95
00:05:18,547 --> 00:05:20,188
I'm the victim, smiling to please.

96
00:05:21,227 --> 00:05:22,028
You knew all along

97
00:05:22,028 --> 00:05:23,068
and pointed a gun at him?

98
00:05:23,467 --> 00:05:24,467
Unloaded gun.

99
00:05:24,828 --> 00:05:25,867
Well, he didn't know that.

100
00:05:30,068 --> 00:05:31,347
You're defending him.

101
00:05:33,148 --> 00:05:34,107
You should make it up.

102
00:05:46,748 --> 00:05:47,268
Let's drink.

103
00:06:00,107 --> 00:06:02,028
Actually, I'm not stupid.

104
00:06:02,188 --> 00:06:03,667
I've more or less figured it out.

105
00:06:05,148 --> 00:06:06,107
But

106
00:06:06,547 --> 00:06:08,347
neither of you told me during this time.

107
00:06:09,188 --> 00:06:10,347
I don't feel right to ask.

108
00:06:11,347 --> 00:06:13,068
Now that we've brought it up today

109
00:06:13,588 --> 00:06:14,588
and no outsiders here,

110
00:06:15,028 --> 00:06:16,508
I'll be bold and ask one more thing.

111
00:06:17,787 --> 00:06:19,148
Why did Feng have to leave

112
00:06:19,148 --> 00:06:20,427
back then?

113
00:06:28,347 --> 00:06:28,948
Mr. Tu,

114
00:06:29,188 --> 00:06:31,427
I didn't know Bai Ruxue worked for Feng.

115
00:06:31,828 --> 00:06:32,907
Lu didn't know either.

116
00:06:34,107 --> 00:06:35,307
He was just trying to help me.

117
00:06:37,028 --> 00:06:38,307
But you know

118
00:06:40,427 --> 00:06:41,427
us two.

119
00:06:46,708 --> 00:06:49,188
After all this, you still call me Lu.

120
00:06:49,867 --> 00:06:51,748
So all my life-risking efforts

121
00:06:51,748 --> 00:06:52,628
were in vain.

122
00:06:55,907 --> 00:06:57,068
Then what should I call you?

123
00:06:57,588 --> 00:06:58,107
Tell me.

124
00:07:00,427 --> 00:07:01,388
Just call me a simp.

125
00:07:01,388 --> 00:07:01,948
Okay?

126
00:07:03,068 --> 00:07:03,787
Alright.

127
00:07:04,467 --> 00:07:06,188
Wish you two lovebirds a happy ending.

128
00:07:06,188 --> 00:07:07,188
Get married soon.

129
00:07:07,188 --> 00:07:08,268
Let's toast together.

130
00:07:08,588 --> 00:07:09,588
Come on, let's drink.

131
00:07:24,667 --> 00:07:25,388
Take a guess.

132
00:07:25,388 --> 00:07:26,388
How many of them?

133
00:07:41,068 --> 00:07:41,748
Scared?

134
00:07:52,867 --> 00:07:53,588
Where's security?

135
00:07:56,467 --> 00:07:57,188
Didn't bring any.

136
00:07:59,748 --> 00:08:01,472
Afraid you'd overthink it,
I didn't either.

137
00:08:02,304 --> 00:08:03,388
I thought you brought it,

138
00:08:03,388 --> 00:08:04,307
so I didn't bring any.

139
00:08:05,948 --> 00:08:06,907
How many bullets?

140
00:08:07,388 --> 00:08:08,188
Fully loaded.

141
00:08:08,427 --> 00:08:09,227
Give me half.

142
00:08:09,987 --> 00:08:10,787
Load it yourself.

143
00:08:13,508 --> 00:08:15,107
Can you handle it? Just give me two.

144
00:08:15,867 --> 00:08:16,987
I'm not as useless as you.

145
00:08:19,188 --> 00:08:19,907
When we fight,

146
00:08:19,907 --> 00:08:21,268
take the way back with Jiasheng.

147
00:08:37,588 --> 00:08:38,547
Murder.

148
00:09:59,947 --> 00:10:00,707
Mr. He,

149
00:10:01,348 --> 00:10:02,067
how was it?

150
00:10:02,748 --> 00:10:03,707
Satisfied?

151
00:10:06,988 --> 00:10:07,827
But

152
00:10:08,827 --> 00:10:09,547
it's a pity

153
00:10:10,028 --> 00:10:11,988
I can't tear them to pieces.

154
00:10:12,388 --> 00:10:13,187
Why didn't you

155
00:10:13,508 --> 00:10:15,268
let me kill them?

156
00:10:15,988 --> 00:10:17,587
Mr. He,

157
00:10:17,947 --> 00:10:19,508
don't be so impatient.

158
00:10:20,427 --> 00:10:22,427
You need to learn to be a cat.

159
00:10:23,348 --> 00:10:25,268
After catching a mouse,

160
00:10:25,587 --> 00:10:28,108
don't be in a hurry to eat it.

161
00:10:28,348 --> 00:10:30,148
Take your time to play with it.

162
00:10:30,148 --> 00:10:31,667
That's what makes it fun.

163
00:10:31,667 --> 00:10:32,187
Alright.

164
00:10:32,667 --> 00:10:33,868
Then next,

165
00:10:34,427 --> 00:10:35,587
what should I do?

166
00:10:37,587 --> 00:10:39,868
You can learn to be a snake.

167
00:10:40,148 --> 00:10:41,947
Just by flicking your tongue,

168
00:10:42,348 --> 00:10:43,787
you can make your opponent

169
00:10:44,028 --> 00:10:45,307
tremble with fear.

170
00:11:16,108 --> 00:11:17,268
Don't move.

171
00:11:24,108 --> 00:11:25,307
Why aren't you hospitalized?

172
00:11:25,587 --> 00:11:26,667
It's just a graze,

173
00:11:26,868 --> 00:11:28,187
but it's a bullet wound.

174
00:11:28,348 --> 00:11:29,988
Should've stayed there for treatment.

175
00:11:32,108 --> 00:11:32,868
You

176
00:11:33,947 --> 00:11:35,108
must be terrified yesterday.

177
00:11:48,348 --> 00:11:50,307
Take this medicine on an empty stomach.

178
00:11:51,108 --> 00:11:52,108
Take it now.

179
00:11:52,388 --> 00:11:53,748
I'll prepare breakfast for you.

180
00:12:01,307 --> 00:12:02,947
When did you learn to drive?

181
00:12:06,176 --> 00:12:07,200
When I wanted to uncover

182
00:12:07,200 --> 00:12:08,707
the real cause of Ruoxi's death.

183
00:12:11,868 --> 00:12:13,348
I answered honestly enough, didn't I?

184
00:12:14,348 --> 00:12:15,508
Then in exchange,

185
00:12:16,348 --> 00:12:18,187
you should answer my questions.

186
00:12:19,148 --> 00:12:19,748
Ask away.

187
00:12:26,148 --> 00:12:27,427
Last night you said

188
00:12:27,947 --> 00:12:30,148
He Mike probably doesn't have the guts.

189
00:12:30,348 --> 00:12:31,388
Who do you think it is?

190
00:12:44,108 --> 00:12:44,907
Feng.

191
00:12:46,108 --> 00:12:46,988
Would he

192
00:12:48,148 --> 00:12:49,268
target even you?

193
00:12:52,587 --> 00:12:55,187
Did something happen between you?

194
00:12:58,547 --> 00:13:00,028
It's a long story.

195
00:13:01,468 --> 00:13:02,067
But I haven't

196
00:13:03,268 --> 00:13:04,587
confirmed it completely.

197
00:13:07,067 --> 00:13:08,108
When I have time,

198
00:13:08,508 --> 00:13:09,388
I'll tell you.

199
00:13:10,067 --> 00:13:10,748
Perhaps

200
00:13:11,268 --> 00:13:12,587
it can explain many problems.

201
00:13:15,468 --> 00:13:16,587
So about the internal

202
00:13:16,587 --> 00:13:18,707
and external troubles you mentioned
on the rooftop,

203
00:13:19,667 --> 00:13:20,628
the internal trouble

204
00:13:21,148 --> 00:13:22,307
refers to Feng.

205
00:13:26,988 --> 00:13:29,187
Now it's not just internal trouble.

206
00:13:31,547 --> 00:13:32,307
External trouble

207
00:13:32,787 --> 00:13:33,907
is right in front of us.

208
00:13:39,667 --> 00:13:40,468
You should rest now.

209
00:13:41,748 --> 00:13:43,067
I'll prepare breakfast for you.

210
00:14:06,148 --> 00:14:08,108
So according to Mr. Tu's analysis,

211
00:14:08,587 --> 00:14:10,028
those who attacked him

212
00:14:10,028 --> 00:14:11,907
appeared to be under He Mike's order,

213
00:14:11,907 --> 00:14:13,028
seeking to avenge his son.

214
00:14:13,228 --> 00:14:14,108
But in reality,

215
00:14:14,108 --> 00:14:15,587
it's Mr. Nie who is behind it.

216
00:14:16,228 --> 00:14:17,108
Mr. Nie?

217
00:14:18,388 --> 00:14:19,587
Nie Feng, the fourth brother.

218
00:14:20,028 --> 00:14:20,628
What about

219
00:14:21,427 --> 00:14:23,547
the eldest, second, and third brothers?

220
00:14:26,268 --> 00:14:28,148
When I arrived at Deep In The Bustle,

221
00:14:28,388 --> 00:14:30,148
I only knew about Mr. Tu
and the other two.

222
00:14:30,628 --> 00:14:31,907
And I haven't met Mr. Nie Feng.

223
00:14:32,587 --> 00:14:33,748
There are two explanations.

224
00:14:34,508 --> 00:14:35,468
One is

225
00:14:35,667 --> 00:14:37,108
that as they swore brotherhood

226
00:14:37,307 --> 00:14:38,348
before Lord Guan,

227
00:14:39,028 --> 00:14:39,787
they acknowledged

228
00:14:39,787 --> 00:14:42,307
Liu Bei, Guan Yu and Zhang Fei
as the eldest, second and third.

229
00:14:42,587 --> 00:14:43,587
Hence they are

230
00:14:43,587 --> 00:14:44,868
the fourth, fifth, and sixth.

231
00:14:45,468 --> 00:14:46,628
So each of them

232
00:14:46,628 --> 00:14:47,787
worships one statue.

233
00:14:48,307 --> 00:14:49,468
According to the order,

234
00:14:49,468 --> 00:14:50,508
Mr. Tu worships

235
00:14:50,508 --> 00:14:51,427
Lord Guan.

236
00:14:52,160 --> 00:14:53,184
Indeed,

237
00:14:53,280 --> 00:14:55,040
inside Room 999 is Lord Guan.

238
00:14:55,468 --> 00:14:57,787
But I find the other explanation
more credible.

239
00:14:58,587 --> 00:15:00,468
The eldest, second,
and third brothers might

240
00:15:00,947 --> 00:15:01,868
be from the Cabinet.

241
00:15:02,187 --> 00:15:03,136
Can't show their faces.

242
00:15:03,667 --> 00:15:05,067
Therefore, we only see

243
00:15:05,067 --> 00:15:06,108
these three brothers.

244
00:15:06,787 --> 00:15:07,508
Then,

245
00:15:07,787 --> 00:15:08,827
why

246
00:15:09,108 --> 00:15:10,628
did Feng go abroad?

247
00:15:13,827 --> 00:15:16,468
I don't have a standard answer for that.

248
00:15:16,608 --> 00:15:18,108
I really don't know.

249
00:15:18,307 --> 00:15:20,827
But it must be related to what they did

250
00:15:21,067 --> 00:15:22,028
behind the scenes.

251
00:15:23,468 --> 00:15:24,988
As far as I know, Ruoxi

252
00:15:25,148 --> 00:15:27,628
argued with Mr. Tu over this.

253
00:15:28,628 --> 00:15:30,348
If I hadn't seen this ledger,

254
00:15:31,547 --> 00:15:33,468
were you planning
to keep hiding the schemes

255
00:15:34,148 --> 00:15:35,947
you three are up to behind the scenes?

256
00:15:43,748 --> 00:15:45,748
Do you know the consequences
of managing all this?

257
00:15:49,547 --> 00:15:50,656
Shoot!

258
00:15:51,988 --> 00:15:52,868
Shoot

259
00:15:54,067 --> 00:15:55,508
and I won't care about anything,

260
00:15:56,547 --> 00:15:57,868
and won't be able to.

261
00:16:06,868 --> 00:16:08,628
Ignore the matters of us three brothers,

262
00:16:09,148 --> 00:16:10,748
especially Feng and me.

263
00:16:11,148 --> 00:16:12,307
Because this is

264
00:16:12,587 --> 00:16:13,427
a very dangerous

265
00:16:13,587 --> 00:16:14,748
and life-threatening matter.

266
00:16:15,707 --> 00:16:16,508
I don't care.

267
00:16:17,148 --> 00:16:18,348
I only want you to be safe.

268
00:16:20,067 --> 00:16:21,228
Only you...

269
00:16:40,667 --> 00:16:41,508
So

270
00:16:41,508 --> 00:16:43,547
what exactly is in that ledger?

271
00:16:44,667 --> 00:16:45,760
Official position trading?

272
00:16:46,067 --> 00:16:46,816
Corrupt deals?

273
00:16:47,307 --> 00:16:48,827
Or human trafficking, or what?

274
00:16:49,187 --> 00:16:50,468
Ruoxi didn't say.

275
00:16:51,028 --> 00:16:52,587
I didn't have the chance to ask her.

276
00:16:53,108 --> 00:16:55,148
But I think

277
00:16:55,148 --> 00:16:56,748
it might really be related

278
00:16:57,988 --> 00:17:00,067
to Mr. Nie leaving Deep In The Bustle.

279
00:17:07,412 --> 00:17:11,086
♪If the heart can't hear the sorrow♪

280
00:17:11,385 --> 00:17:14,576
♪It only makes everything look so fake♪

281
00:17:16,408 --> 00:17:20,029
♪Your eyes resemble hers too much♪

282
00:17:20,578 --> 00:17:23,377
♪Who makes me forget whom♪

283
00:17:24,848 --> 00:17:28,578
♪The warmth in my heart is fading♪

284
00:17:28,802 --> 00:17:32,299
♪Every glance feels like atonement♪

285
00:17:33,698 --> 00:17:37,385
♪Ambiguity hidden in the night breeze♪

286
00:17:38,023 --> 00:17:43,138
♪Blows away the chance to explain♪

287
00:17:43,842 --> 00:17:47,976
♪I feel guilty♪

288
00:17:48,546 --> 00:17:52,290
♪I'll have no regrets
even I leave quietly♪

289
00:17:53,154 --> 00:17:56,597
♪Even in tears♪

